            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#烫伤抹牙膏会影响伤口愈合#】#暑期儿童意外伤害高发#，烧烫伤、切割伤、跌落、溺水等时有发生。医生提醒，①应对轻微划伤，家中可常备碘伏和金霉素眼药...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%83%AB%E4%BC%A4%E6%8A%B9%E7%89%99%E8%86%8F%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%BC%A4%E5%8F%A3%E6%84%88%E5%90%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%83%AB%E4%BC%A4%E6%8A%B9%E7%89%99%E8%86%8F%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%BC%A4%E5%8F%A3%E6%84%88%E5%90%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#烫伤抹牙膏会影响伤口愈合#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9A%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%91%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9A%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%91%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#暑期儿童意外伤害高发#</span></a>，烧烫伤、切割伤、跌落、溺水等时有发生。医生提醒，①应对轻微划伤，家中可常备碘伏和金霉素眼药膏；②烧烫伤应凉水冲洗至少15-30分钟，千万不要在创面上涂抹牙膏、锅灰、蜂蜜等，可能影响伤口愈合；③婴幼儿误服药物不建议催吐，应带上误服药物尽快到医院就诊👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4931785092431874" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hgn4t3ns5lj60sc0fxakf02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/EI1Ta0Ovlx087AVYVKj6010412013V3F0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691486133&amp;ssig=BG6qFIlsKA&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/VLbQbG1Xlx087AVV5Qhq01041200zYWi0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691486133&amp;ssig=EnzRHWpYG6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/gFsaIeoOlx087AVWmckU01041200mUqf0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691486133&amp;ssig=gDKJaDbOYj&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4931785092431874&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
